      <h4>Why PGPBA?</h4>
      <p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
     
The Great Lakes' Post Graduate Programme in Business Analytics is designed for executives who want to build their careers in the analytics industry. The programme covers essentials of business management, deep dives into the study of business analytics and provides hands on training on analytical tools and technologies that are used by companies worldwide.
</p><p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
Some of the unique features of the programme are enlisted below: 
The curriculum provides a detailed study in analytics alongwith covering general management subjects and specialised domain areas such as Retail, BFSI, Healthcare, E-commerce and Energy. 
</p><p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
The courses are taught by eminent faculty from Great Lakes and senior executives from leading analytics companies.
</p><p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
The programme provides the candidates with hands on exposure to tools such as SAS, Tableau and actual industry case studies through virtual labs, assignments and project
</p><p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
The blended delivery model (classroom and online) of the programme makes it convenient for working professionals to attend classroom sessions without having to quit their jobs and also, pace their learning through online sessions.    </p>
<h4>Who is it for?</h4>
<p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">

The PGP-BA programme is designed for working professionals who wish to embark on managerial careers in the analytics sector. The prior experience of a candidate need not be in analytics, though an analytic bent of mind would be preferable. A successful graduate degree, a minimum experience of two years and a keen interest in analytical problem solving are the only pre-requisites for applying to the programme. 
</p>
<h4>Career paths after PGPBA</h4>
<p style="float: left;padding: 20px 15px;width: 95%;text-align: justify;">
The Post Graduate Programme in Business Analytics (PGP-BA) equips you with the relevant knowledge and skills to pursue managerial careers with best of analytics companies or move the analytics roles within your existing organisation.
Though the roles would vary across organizations and would also depend on a candidate's experience levels, some of the indicative roles would be: Business Analyst / Senior Business Analyst, Manager (Analytics), Head (Analytics), Vice President (Analytics), Consultant, etc.
